OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out this evening, otherwise a
OL,7,Fdry end to the day. Then the rest of
OL,8,Fthe night will be dry with clear
OL,9,Fperiods.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMostly dry with variable
OL,12,Famounts of cloud, the odd shower
OL,13,Facross the Southern Uplands. A few
OL,14,Fshowers breaking out in the evening
OL,15,Felsewhere.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,18,FScattered showers on Tuesday, slow
OL,19,Fmoving and heavy by afternoon. Drier
OL,20,Fon Wednesday with fewer showers. Early
OL,21,Frain on Thursday then dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
